OL,3,CWhat Northern Ireland council area has
OL,4,Cthe most potholes?
OL,6,FPotholes have been posing a persistent
OL,7,Fproblem for road users, and for some
OL,8,Fmore than others.
OL,10,FFigures released by the Department for
OL,11,FInfrastructure show that Newry, Mourne
OL,12,Fand Down District Council area ranked
OL,13,Fhighest across all council areas for
OL,14,Fthe number of potholes recorded in
OL,15,F2023.
OL,17,F20,080 were recorded compared to
OL,18,F15,214 in 2022. The council area
OL,19,Franked highest then too.
