OL,6,F12,986 were recorded in across Armagh,
OL,7,FBanbridge and Craigavon Council, a
OL,8,Fdrop from the previous year when
OL,9,F14,916 were recorded, however, it
OL,10,Fstill came in second place.
OL,12,FCastlereagh and Lisburn City Council
OL,13,Franked lowest, registering just under
OL,14,F5,000 potholes.
OL,16,FOn Monday, Infrastructure Minister
OL,17,FJohn O'Dowd announced an additional
OL,18,F#1m in funding to address the issue.
