OL,6,F"Unfortunately, a number of factors
OL,7,Fhas recently made the situation worse.
OL,8,FFor the last decade the Department has
OL,9,Fbeen operating in a challenging
OL,10,Ffinancial position due to British
OL,11,FGovernment cuts and austerity which
OL,12,Fhas had an impact on road maintenance
OL,13,Factivities and the overall condition
OL,14,Fof the road network.
OL,16,F"Add to that, the impact of climate
OL,17,Fchange, with the wettest October in
OL,18,Fover 153 years of records, which
OL,19,Fcaused severe damage to some roads
OL,20,Facross the North.
